data.description: Hey you, yes you....the one that is reading this, did you know this home qualifies for ZERO downpayment loan! That's right, this 4 bedroom home located in Healdton, Ok could be yours for NO MONEY out of your pocket! If you are looking for a starter home or a rental to add to your portfolio this property is the one for you! The master bedroom and laundry room are off the living room separate from the other bedrooms. There is plenty of storage in the garage and  a large fenced in backyard with storage building. Call today to find out how to make this home yours!
